Homework 2: Scene in 3D
Khaled Hossain
CSCI 5229 Summer 2023

Create a simple scene that isviewable in three projection modes:

1. Overhead orthogonal;
2. Overhead perspective;
3. First person perspective.

It contains 3 houses, 3 trees, a sun made using different shapes.

Key bindings
m Toggle between perspective, orthogonal & first person
+/- Changes field of view for perspective  
 arrows Change view angle  
 ESC Exit
In First Person mode (mode = 2):
W,A,S,D To move position of camera forward, backward, left & right
Arrows Rotate camera

Time taken to complete 6 hours

Compile and run instructions

- make
- ./hw2.exe
